# lex

> Lexical analyzer generator
> Given the specification for a lexical analyzer, generates C code implementing it
> More information: https://manned.org/lex.1

- Generate an analyzer from a Lex file:

`lex {string value: analyzer.l}`

- Specify the output file:

`lex {string value: analyzer.l} --outfile {string value: analyzer.c}`

- Compile a C file generated by Lex:

`cc {string value: path/to/lex.yy.c} --output {string value: executable}`
